# Implementing Pebble: A Language Implementation Tutorial in Zig

Welcome! This tutorial will guide you through building an interpreter for **Pebble**, a simple variable-based scripting language. Along the way, you'll learn Zig fundamentals and core concepts of language implementation.

We'll build this incrementally. Each section introduces a small piece, explains *why* it works that way, and connects it to the bigger picture.

